ia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Abhinav Bindra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's an incredibly tough situation.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Frankly, I do not even know what to say.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean the rules are very clear - where you draw a line.\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport is always governed by the rules.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not govern sport by rules, there is no sport,\\\" Abhinav Bindra told India Today.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Abhinav Bindra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\"}, {\"begin\": 1110, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_Today\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.539737469838979e-25, \"text\": \"India Today\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bindra does not have a clue about the direction in which the case is heading but he too is keeping his fingers crossed.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\